References don't work.

1692
01:57:46,460 --> 01:57:49,418
- But shortcuts will!
- Bauua Singh.

1693
01:57:49,418 --> 01:57:51,251
- Who is Bauua Singh?
- Present!

1694
01:57:51,585 --> 01:57:54,210
- Here you go, sir.
- Blind man coming.

1695
